graph LR
    TrustyAI[TrustyAI Service Operator]

    %% External Dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes v1.19+]
    TrustyAI -->|routes & OAuth| OpenShift[OpenShift v4.6+]
    TrustyAI -->|metrics CRD| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator v0.64.1]
    TrustyAI -->|InferenceService CRD| KServe[KServe v0.11.0]

    %% Internal RHOAI Dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|watches/patches InferenceServices| KServeInt[KServe]
    TrustyAI -->|injects payload processors| ModelMesh[ModelMesh]
    TrustyAI -->|exposes metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[RHOAI Dashboard] -.->|UI integration| TrustyAI
    DSP[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|model monitoring| TrustyAI

    %% External Services
    TrustyAI -->|API server| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API]
    TrustyAI -->|authentication| OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth]
    TrustyAI -->|TLS certificates| ServiceCA[service-ca-operator]

    %% Data Flow
    KServeInt -->|inference payloads| TrustyAI
    ModelMesh -->|inference payloads| TrustyAI

